com.soa.auth.callback

Interface ISAMLCallback

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javax.security.auth.callback.Callback
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SAMLCallback

    public interface ISAMLCallback
extends javax.security.auth.callback.Callback
    This is the Callback interface for collecting SAML assertion. SAML assertion can be in the format of java Assertion object, XML Node, and byte stream.
